snippet.title: Rain City | Gameplay Trailer | Nintendo Switch
snippet.description:
The rain never stops in Rain City, where the animals live.

You are a cat that has just arrived to the city in search of your missing sister.
Venture yourself into this game filled with puzzles and adventures.


To be released in Nintendo Switch during the 2019 rain season, July 27.
Playstation 4 TBD

©2019 BIG PINEAPPLE / Cotton Game.
Published by ORENDA Inc.
